Sentencas: The study elementarily investigated the effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Four single cells were fabricated with different cathode structures, and the total cathode thickness was 15, 55, 85, and 85 mu m for cell-A, cell-B, cell-C, and cell-D, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cell-A, cell-B, and cell-D included only one cathode layer, which was fabricated by (La0.74Bi0.10Sr0.16)MnO3-delta (LBSM) electrode material.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The cathode of the cell-C was composed of a (La0.74Bi0.10Sr0.16)MnO3-delta - (Bi0.7Er0.3O1.5) (L B S M - ESB) cathode functional layer and a LBSM cathode layer.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Different cathode structures leaded to dissimilar polarization character for the four cells.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 750 degrees C, the total polarization resistance (R-p) of the cell-A was 1.11, 0.41 and 0.53 Omega cm(2) at the current of 0, 400, and 800 mA, respectively, and that of the cell-B was 1.10, 0.39, and 0.23 Omega cm(2) at the current of 0, 400, and 800 mA, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For cell-C and cell-D, their polarization character was similar to that of the cell-B and R-p also decreased with the increase of the current.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum power density was 0.81, 1.01, 0.79, and 0.43 W cm(-2) at 750 degrees C for cell-D, cell-C, cell-B, and cell-A, respectively.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results demonstrated that cathode structures evidently influenced the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Effect of the cathode structure on the electrochemical performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells
